; diskboot.config entry for nvme.device boot-drive integration.
;
; Append this line to Kickstart:diskboot.config (or to the
; diskboot.config inside your kickstart.zip on QEMU) so that the
; diskboot.kmod module scans the NVMe controller for mountable
; partitions at boot time.
;
;    <device name>      <unit>  <flags>
nvme.device              1        1
